nt advisory\u2192blocking hook added \u2014 SIC evidenceDomains > 2 triggers per-domain evidence-gathering fan-out enforcement (rule 28 v1.0.0; canonical plan v2 \u00a74 row 5.14). PR 5.15: evidence-domain-coverage-gate PreToolUse hook added \u2014 fires on DTC-mutating MCP tools (apply_edit_function / commit_edits / ontology_context_query); derives evidence-domains from SIC.affectedSurfaces[] top-level path segments; asserts OntologyContextSeed.supportingResearchRefs \u22651 ref per domain; advisory after 1st miss, blocking after 2nd; bypass PALANTIR_MINI_EVIDENCE_DOMAIN_COVERAGE_BYPASS=1 (per canonical plan v2 \u00a74 row 5.15).",
